  "stem": "<p>In <math><mo>&#9651;</mo><mi>P</mi><mi>Q</mi><mi>R</mi></math>, <math><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>Q</mi></math> is a right angle and the length of <math><mover><mrow><mi>Q</mi><mi>R</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover></math> is <math><mn>100</mn></math> millimeters. If <math><mi>cos</mi><mi>P</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>3</mn><mn>5</mn></mfrac></math>, what is the length, in millimeters, of <math><mover><mrow><mi>P</mi><mi>Q</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover></math>?</p>",
